company_backgroud_text: test_p APP is a leading telemedicine platform dedicated to connecting patients with healthcare professionals. Founded in 2024, test_p aims to revolutionize the way medical consultations are conducted by leveraging technology to provide accessible and efficient healthcare services.
mission_text: Our mission is to bridge the gap between patients and healthcare providers by offering reliable and convenient online medical consultations. We strive to enhance the quality of healthcare delivery through innovation and commitment to patient well-being.
vision_text: To be the most trusted and user-friendly telemedicine platform in the region, ensuring that everyone has access to quality medical advice and services anytime, anywhere.
service_overview_sub1_text: Connect with specialists via video and chat.
service_overview_sub2_text: Receive digital prescriptions sent directly to your device.
service_overview_sub3_text: Regular follow-ups to track and maintain your health

service_description: test_p APP offers a range of telemedicine services designed to provide convenient and efficient healthcare solutions.
video_description: Connect with certified specialists through secure video calls.
chat_description: Get medical advice and support via our in-app chat feature.
digital_description: Receive prescriptions electronically, which can be sent directly to your preferred pharmacy.
medication_description: Keep track of your medications and receive reminders for refills.
checkin_description: Schedule periodic follow-ups to monitor your health status.
report_description: Access detailed reports on your health metrics and progress.
mental_health_description: Access to mental health professionals for counseling and support.
chronic_disease_description: Ongoing support and management plans for chronic conditions.
scheduling_description: Easily book and manage your appointments.
records_description: Securely store and access your medical history and records within the app.
benefits_description: Unlimited consultations, priority support, and access to exclusive health resources.
future_healthcare: Experience the future of healthcare with test_p APP—where your health is our priority.
service_cancellation_refund_text: Subscribers have the right to cancel the service and request a refund if they have not benefited from it.
package_upgrades_text: Clients can upgrade their packages at any time. All contents and benefits of the current package will be accounted for and transferred to the upgraded package.
package_downgrades_text: If a client chooses to downgrade their package, the contents and benefits of the current package will be carried forward to the new package, where applicable.
service_delivery_gurantee_text: test_p is committed to protecting the rights of its clients. If the requested service is not delivered as promised, appropriate compensation will be provided to ensure client satisfaction.
policy_fairness: This policy ensures fairness and transparency while prioritizing client satisfaction and rights.
hippa_heading: The Health Insurance Portability and Accountability Act (HIPAA)
hippa_value: The Health Insurance Portability and Accountability Act (HIPAA) is a U.S. federal law enacted in 1996 to regulate the use, disclosure, and protection of protected health information (PHI). It applies to healthcare providers, insurers, clearinghouses, and their business associates.
hippa_v1: Protect patient's medical records and personal health information.
hippa_v2: Ensure secure handling of electronic protected health information (ePHI).
hippa_v3: Streamline healthcare administration and reduce costs.
hippa_v4: Give patients control over their personal health data.
delete_policy_intro_value: This policy aims to clarify the process for deleting personal accounts for users of the paid service and how associated data will be handled to ensure compliance with regulations and laws.
delete_policy_note_value: Account deletion is a permanent action, and it will not be possible to recover the account or its associated data after the process is completed.
affected_data_1: Deleting the account will result in the removal of all personal data associated with the service, such as records, subscriptions, and archives.
affected_data_2: Some necessary data may be retained for legal or accounting purposes in accordance with local regulations.
paid_subscription_1: If the account includes an active subscription, the subscription will be automatically terminated upon account deletion.
paid_subscription_2: Paid amounts are non-refundable unless otherwise specified in the terms and conditions.
